@hmg65 ... is this still a work in progress? Just asking, because the PR seems a bit old (3 weeks) and you have newer PRs queued up. If this is still relevant then maybe fix this one first before you move on to newer stuff. Or, if it's not relevant anymore then please close it.
Also: please format title properly if this PR is still relevant.
Thanks

> 

I was thinking we can add an extra `<includeAll path="custom-changelog/"/>` which would looking for the `custom-changelog` directory on the classpath (also we can use `searchPath` of liquibase as well to define multiple search path) and execute any changelog be found by alphabetical order and if the path is missing it will ignore by default.

@vidakovic @galovics What do you think?
